ms)</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <span>200</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> </ti-multicolumn-list-row><ti-multicolumn-list-row> <ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <span>Watchdog timer WDI (s)</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <span>None</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> </ti-multicolumn-list-row><ti-multicolumn-list-row> <ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <span>Supply voltage (min) (V)</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <span>1.1</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> </ti-multicolumn-list-row><ti-multicolumn-list-row> <ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <span>Supply voltage (max) (V)</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <span>6</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> </ti-multicolumn-list-row><ti-multicolumn-list-row> <ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <span>Operating temperature range (°C)</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <span>-40 to 125</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> </ti-multicolumn-list-row> </ti-multicolumn-list> </div> </div> </ti-tab-panel> <ti-tab-panel tab-title="Package | Pins | Size" tab-id="pps" data-di-id="tab-pps" data-ti-di-track="" data-lid="folder_product_details_package" data-navtitle="Package | Pins | Size" > <ti-multicolumn-list row-dividers="true" compact="true" class="u-fullWidth u-margin-bottom-2" > <ti-multicolumn-list-row > <ti-multicolumn-list-cell style="width: 34%" > <a data-navtitle="package_pins-SOT-23 (DBZ)" href="//www.ti.com/lit/pdf/mpds108g" id="pps_1" target="_blank" >SOT-23 (DBZ)</a> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <ti-multicolumn-list-cell style="width: 21%" > <span>3</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> <ti-multicolumn-list-cell style="width: 45%"> <span>6.9204 mm² 2.92 x 2.37</span> </ti-multicolumn-list-cell> </ti-multicolumn-list-row> </ti-multicolumn-list> </ti-tab-panel> <ti-tab-panel tab-title="Features" tab-id="features" data-di-id="tab-features" data-ti-di-track="" data-lid="folder_product_details_features" data-navtitle="Features" > <ti-view-more expand-action-label="View all" collapse-action-label="View less" locale="en-US" class="u-margin-bottom-2 u-hide-only-on-phone" collapsed-height="540" data-ti-di-track="" data-di-id="view-all-params" > <div><ul> <li>3-Pin SOT23 Package</li> <li>Supply Current: 9 µA (Typical)</li> <li>Precision Supply Voltage Monitor: 2.5 V, 3 V, 3.3 V, 5 V</li> <li>Power-On Reset Generator with Fixed Delay Time of 200 ms</li> <li>Pin-for-Pin Compatible with MAX803</li> <li>Temperature Range: –40°C to +125°C</li> <li>Open-Drain, <span style="text-decoration: overline">RESET</span> Output</li> </ul></div> </ti-view-more> <div class="u-show-only-on-phone"> <div><ul> <li>3-Pin SOT23 Package</li> <li>Supply Current: 9 µA (Typical)</li> <li>Precision Supply Voltage Monitor: 2.5 V, 3 V, 3.3 V, 5 V</li> <li>Power-On Reset Generator with Fixed Delay Time of 200 ms</li> <li>Pin-for-Pin Compatible with MAX803</li> <li>Temperature Range: –40°C to +125°C</li> <li>Open-Drain, <span style="text-decoration: overline">RESET</span> Output</li> </ul></div> </div> </ti-tab-panel> <ti-tab-panel tab-title="Description" tab-id="description" data-di-id="tab-description" data-ti-di-track="" data-lid="folder_product_details_description" data-navtitle="Description" > <ti-view-more expand-action-label="View all" collapse-action-label="View less" locale="en-US" class="u-margin-bottom-2 u-hide-only-on-phone" collapsed-height="540" data-ti-di-track="" data-di-id="view-all-params" > <p><p>The TLV8x3 family of supervisory circuits provides circuit initialization and timing supervision, primarily for DSPs and processor-based systems.</p><p>The TLV803, TLV853, and TLV863 are functionally equivalent. The TLV853 and TLV863 provide an alternate pinout of the TLV803. The newer <a href="http://www.ti.com/lit/pdf/SLVSES2">TLV803E</a> device is a pin-to-pin alternative to all of these 3.</p><p>During power on, <span style="text-decoration: overline">RESET</span> asserts when the supply voltage (V<sub>DD</sub>) exceeds 1.1 V. Thereafter, the supervisory circuit monitors V<sub>DD</sub> and keeps <span style="text-decoration: overline">RESET</span> active as long as V<sub>DD</sub> remains below the threshold voltage V<sub>IT</sub>. An internal timer delays the return of the output to the inactive state (high) to ensure proper system reset. The delay time (t<sub>d(typ)</sub> = 200 ms) starts after V<sub>DD</sub> exceeds the threshold voltage, V<sub>IT</sub>. When the supply voltage drops below the V<sub>IT</sub> threshold voltage, the output is active (low) again. All the devices in this family have a fixed sense-threshold voltage (V<sub>IT</sub>) set by an internal voltage divider.</p><p>The product spectrum is designed for supply voltages of 2.5 V, 3 V, 3.3 V, and 5 V. These devices are available in a 3-pin SOT-23 package. The TLV803 devices are characterized for operation over a temperature range of &ndash;40&deg;C to +125&deg;C.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p> </ti-view-more> <div class="u-show-only-on-phone"> <p><p>The TLV8x3 family of supervisory circuits provides circuit initialization and timing supervision, primarily for DSPs and processor-based systems.</p><p>The TLV803, TLV853, and TLV863 are functionally equivalent. The TLV853 and TLV863 provide an alternate pinout of the TLV803. The newer <a href="http://www.ti.com/lit/pdf/SLVSES2">TLV803E</a> device is a pin-to-pin alternative to all of these 3.</p><p>During power on, <span style="text-decoration: overline">RESET</span> asserts when the supply voltage (V<sub>DD</sub>) exceeds 1.1 V. Thereafter, the supervisory circuit monitors V<sub>DD</sub> and keeps <span style="text-decoration: overline">RESET</span> active as long as V<sub>DD</sub> remains below the threshold voltage V<sub>IT</sub>. An internal timer delays the return of the output to the inactive state (high) to ensure proper system reset. The delay time (t<sub>d(typ)</sub> = 200 ms) starts after V<sub>DD</sub> exceeds the threshold voltage, V<sub>IT</sub>. When the supply voltage drops below the V<sub>IT</sub> threshold voltage, the output is active (low) again. All the devices in this family have a fixed sense-threshold voltage (V<sub>IT</sub>) set by an internal voltage divider.</p><p>The product spectrum is designed for supply voltages of 2.5 V, 3 V, 3.3 V, and 5 V. These devices are available in a 3-pin SOT-23 package. The TLV803 devices are characterized for operation over a temperature range of &ndash;40&deg;C to +125&deg;C.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p> </div> </ti-tab-panel> </ti-tab-container> <div class="u-margin-top-6"> <a href="/product-category/power-management/supervisor-reset-ics/reset-watchdog/products.html" class="ti_p-iconText" data-ti-di-track="" data-di-id="find_other_parts"> <span class="ti_p-iconText-icon"><ti-svg-icon appearance="secondary" size="s" icon-set="actions">filter</ti-svg-icon></span> <span>Find other Reset & watchdog ICs</span> </a> </div> </div> <div class="ti_p-col-5 ti_p-col-phone-12"> <ti-media-gallery> <span slot="download-label">Download</span> <span slot="video-transcript-link-text">View video with transcript</span> <span slot="dialog-title-video">Video</span> <ti-video-player slot="media" api-url="/bin/ti/folder/video?locale=en-us&amp;type=genericpart&amp;id=64/527/393475/49483&amp;host_type=media-gallery" data-lid="media gallery" single-video-player lazy="false" data-media-type="video" locale="en-US" > <video-js id="ti-media-gallery-video-1" data-embed="default" controls="" class="vjs-fluid" style="height:100%; padding: 0" ></video-js> </ti-video-player> <ti-image slot="media" alt="3-pin (DBZ) package image" src="/content/dam/ticom/images/products/package/d/dbz0003a.png:small" src-lg="/content/dam/ticom/images/products/package/d/dbz0003a.png:large" data-media-type="image" data-media-name="dbz0003a.png" data-media-desc="3-pin (DBZ) package image" data-media-thumbnail-url="/content/dam/ticom/images/products/package/d/dbz0003a.png:small" data-media-image-url="/content/dam/ticom/images/products/package/d/dbz0003a.png:large" ></ti-image> </ti-media-gallery> </div> </div> </div> <div> <div class="ti_p-row"> <ti-card wide="callout" responsive="true" data-lid="folder_product_similar_products" class="ti_p-col"> <div class="u-flex mod-align-center"> <h3 class="u-margin-bottom-6">Similar products you might be interested in</h3> <div class="u-hide-only-on-phone u-font-size-medium u-font-weight-normal u-margin-left-6 u-margin-bottom-6"> <ti-svg-icon icon-set="actions" size="s" appearance="secondary">open-in-new</ti-svg-icon> <a href="/compare-products/?id=393475&amp;type=GPT&amp;mode=alternate-gpn&amp;partList=TLV863M,TLV803E&amp;sticky=true" class="ti-product-snapshot-cta u-padding-left-2" target="_blank" data-navtitle="Compare alternates" >Compare alternates</a> </div> </div> <div> <ti-view-more use-button collapse-action-label="View less" expand-action-label="View all 1" collapsed-height="368" > <div class="ti_p-productSynopsisList_container"> <div class="ti_p-productSynopsisList_section" > <h5 class="ti_p-productSynopsisList_heading">Drop-in replacement with upgraded functionality to the compared device</h5> <section role="list" class="ti_p-productSynopsisList_item-list"> <div role="listitem"> <div> <ti-product-synopsis data-lid="similar_products" product-url="/product/TLV803E" image-url="/content/dam/ticom/images/products/package/d/dbz0003a.png:singlesmall" default-image="//www.ti.com/content/dam/ticom/images/icons/svg-icons/processor-chip-icon.svg" > <!-- NEW badge --> <!-- Product title --> <a slot="product-link" href="//www.ti.com/product/TLV803E" >TLV803E</a> <!-- Lifecycle badge --> <ti-product-status slot="product-status" compact status="1" tooltip="This product has been released to the market and is available for purchase. For some products, newer alternatives may be available."> <a href="/support-quality/quality-policies-procedures/product-life-cycle.html" data-navtitle="ACTIVE">ACTIVE</a> </ti-product-status> <span slot="description" class="u-paragraph-medium">Low-power voltage supervisor (reset IC) with active-low open-drain output</span> <span slot="comment" class="u-paragraph-medium u-margin-bottom-0">Lower quiescent current (250nA) in more fixed threshold voltage options</span> </ti-product-synopsis> </div> </div> </section> </div> </div> </ti-view-more> </div> </ti-card> </div> </div> </section> <section class="ti_p-page-responsive ti_p-layout-space-large"> <div class="ti_p-row"> <div class="ti_p-col-12"> <h3 navbar-id="tech-docs" navbar-name="Technical documentation" data-navtitle="Technical documentation" class="u-header-2">Technical documentation</h3> <div> <div class="ti_p-row"> <div class="ti_p-col-12"> <div class="u-margin-bottom-4 u-margin-left-2"> <span class="ti_p-iconText"> <span class="ti_p-iconText-icon"> <ti-svg-icon appearance="tertiary" size="s">star</ti-svg-icon> </span> <span>=<em class="u-margin-left-2">Top documentation for this product selected by TI</em></span> </span> </div> <ti-techdocs data-lid="folder_product_technical_documents" doc-type-all-label="All" doc-type-all-value="All" search-placeholder="Filter title by keyword" metrics-name="folder_product" > <div slot="error-message" style="height: 60px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8" class="u-flex mod-justify-center mod-align-center" >No results found. Please clear your search and try again.</div> <span slot="show-all-label">View all 2</span> <table> <colgroup> <col /> <col /> <col /> <col /> <col /> </colgroup> <thead> <tr> <th prop-key="featured">Top documentation</th> <th prop-key="type">Type</th> <th prop-key="title">Title</th> <th prop-key="pdf-html">Format options</th> <th prop-key="date">Date</th> </tr> </thead> <tbody> <tr> <td>*</td> <td doc-type="Data sheet">Data sheet</td> <td > <a href="/lit/gpn/tlv863m" data-navtitle="Data sheet|Featured|TLV863M" data-di-id="tech_doc_title_1" target="_blank">TLV8x3 3-Pin Voltage Supervisors with Active-Low, Open-Drain Reset datasheet (Rev. E)</a> </td> <td> <a href="/lit/gpn/tlv863m" target="_blank" data-navtitle="Data sheet|Featured|TLV863M|PDF">PDF</a> <span>|</span> <a href="/document-viewer/tlv863m/datasheet" target="_blank" data-navtitle="Data sheet|Featured|TLV863M|HTML">HTML</a> </td> <td utc-date="2020-12-30T00:00:00.000Z">30 Dec 2020</td> </tr> <tr> <td></td> <td doc-type="E-book">E-book</td> <td > <a href="/lit/pdf/slyy167" data-navtitle="E-book|SLYY167" data-di-id="tech_doc_title_2" target="_blank">Voltage Supervisor and Reset ICs: Tips, Tricks and Basics</a> </td> <td> </td> <td utc-date="2019-06-28T00:00:00.000Z">28 Jun 2019</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </ti-techdocs> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class="ti_p-page-responsive ti_p-layout-space-large"> <div class="ti_p-row"> <div class="ti_p-col-12"> <span navbar-id="desKit"></span> <span navbar-id="all"></span> <span navbar-id="hardware-development"></span> <span navbar-id="software-development"></span> <span navbar-id="design-tools-simulation"></span> <span navbar-id="reference-designs"></span> <span navbar-id="cad-cae-symbols"></span> <h3 class="u-header-2" navbar-name="Design &amp; development" data-navtitle="Design &amp; development" navbar-id="design-development">Design &amp; development</h3> <!-- Case to check for processors --> <p>For additional terms or required resources, click any title below to view the detail page where available.</p> </div> </div> <div> <script type="text/javascript"> /*<![CDATA[*/ var headerCurrency = document.querySelector('ti-header-currency-selection'); var headerLanguage = document.querySelector('ti-header-language-selection'); var userCurrency = 'USD'; var userLocale = 'en-US'; if (headerCurrency) { var currency = headerCurrency.getAttribute('value'); if (currency) { userCurrency = currency; } } if (headerLanguage) { var locale = headerLanguage.getAttribute('value'); if (locale) { userLocale = locale; } } var currencyFormat = { convertAndFormat: function(value) { return value; } }; var setCurrencyFormat = function() { if (typeof currencyFormat.getInstance === 'undefined') { const win = typeof window !== 'undefined' ? window : {}; if (win.com && win.com.TI && win.com.TI.CurrencyFormat) { currencyFormat = win.com.TI.CurrencyFormat; updateAssetPricing(); } } }; var updateAssetPricing = function () { var assetsPricing = {} || {}; var exchangeRateMap = "{\"TWD\":31.69300884,\"CHF\":0.78009996,\"MXN\":17.62642554,\"EUR\":0.86065926,\"CAD\":1.36229945,\"MYR\":3.95350676,\"ZAR\":16.49865536,\"NOK\":9.6556785,\"INR\":91.7549043,\"VND\":26219.19244887,\"CNY\":6.91161428,\"THB\":31.97902176,\"AUD\":1.42775557,\"KRW\":1486.50255678,\"ILS\":3.07579686,\"JPY\":157.95991609,\"GBP\":0.74816699,\"IDR\":16909.02942171,\"NZD\":1.68833361,\"PHP\":59.02386335,\"TRY\":43.99665625,\"RUB\":79.09202357}" ? JSON.parse("{\"TWD\":31.69300884,\"CHF\":0.78009996,\"MXN\":17.62642554,\"EUR\":0.86065926,\"CAD\":1.36229945,\"MYR\":3.95350676,\"ZAR\":16.49865536,\"NOK\":9.6556785,\"INR\":91.7549043,\"VND\":26219.19244887,\"CNY\":6.91161428,\"THB\":31.97902176,\"AUD\":1.42775557,\"KRW\":1486.50255678,\"ILS\":3.07579686,\"JPY\":157.95991609,\"GBP\":0.74816699,\"IDR\":16909.02942171,\"NZD\":1.68833361,\"PHP\":59.02386335,\"TRY\":43.99665625,\"RUB\":79.09202357}") : { 'USD' : 1 }; var priceSlots = document.getElementsByName('js-asset-price') || []; priceSlots.forEach(function (slot) { var assetPrice = assetsPricing[slot.dataset.assetid]; if (assetPrice) { var formattedPrice = currencyFormat.convertAndFormat(assetPrice, exchangeRateMap[userCurrency] ? exchangeRateMap[userCurrency] : 1, false, exchangeRateMap[userCurrency] ? userCurrency : 'USD', userLocale); slot.textContent = exchangeRateMap[userCurrency] ? formattedPrice + ' (' + userCurrency +')' : formattedPrice + ' (USD)'; } }); }; var currencyUpdate = function(e) { userCurrency = (typeof (e.detail) !== "undefined" && typeof (e.detail) !== null) ? e.detail : 'USD'; updateAssetPricing(); }; var localeUpdate = function(e) { userLocale = (typeof (e.detail) !== "undefined" && typeof (e.detail) !== null) ? e.detail.locale : 'en-US'; updateAssetPricing(); }; /** * Called after page load, gets inventory from service, and updates front end accordingly. */ var loadToolsInventory = function () { var toolsList = null; if (toolsList != null && toolsList.length > 0) { var url = '/productmodel/opn/tistoresegmented'; var headers = new Headers(); headers.append('Content-Type', 'application/json'); /* the api endpoint only allows a max of 5 OPNs to be fetched, so we may need to fetch in groups */ var inventoryPromises = []; var start = 0; while (start < toolsList.length) { var end = start + 5; var body = JSON.stringify(toolsList.slice(start, end)); inventoryPromises.push( fetch(url, { method: 'POST', headers: headers, body: body }) ); start = end; } /* wait for all fetches to complete */ Promise.all(inventoryPromises).then(function (responses) { var toolsInventory = {}; var loginRequired = false; var jsonPromises = []; responses.forEach(function (response) { if (response.ok && response.status === 200) { jsonPromises.push(response.json()); } else if (response.status === 401) { loginRequired = true; } else { console.warn('Failed to fetch tool inventory:', response.status); } }); /* wait for json data from all fetches */ Promise.all(jsonPromises).then(function (json) { json.forEach(function (data) { Object.keys(data).forEach(function (opn) { toolsInventory[opn] = data[opn]; }); }); if (loginRequired) { setLoginRequired(toolsList); } else if (Object.keys(toolsInventory).length > 0) { setToolsInventory(toolsList, toolsInventory); } else { /* unknown issue - show "not available" */ setToolsUnavailable(toolsList); } }); }).catch(function (error) { setLoginRequired(toolsList); }); } }; /** * Apply inventory service results. */ var setToolsInventory = function (toolsList, toolsInventoryMap) { var inStockText = "In stock"; var outOfStockText = "Out of stock on TI.com"; toolsList.forEach(function (opn) { var toolInventory = toolsInventoryMap[opn]; if (!toolInventory) { /* no store inventory record - remove the dom */ var el = document.getElementById(opn + '-available'); el && el.parentElement.removeChild(el); } else { var availableEl = document.getElementById(opn + '-available'); /* make sure dom exists */ if (availableEl) { var el = document.getElementById(opn + '-order'); el.parentElement.removeChild(el); el = document.getElementById(opn + '-view'); el.parentElement.removeChild(el); el = document.getElementById(opn + '-unavailable'); el.parentElement.removeChild(el); var inventory = toolInventory.inventory; if (inventory > 0) { /* in stock */ var orderLimit = toolInventory.orderLimit; el = document.getElementById(opn + '-cart'); el.orderLimit = orderLimit; el = document.getElementById(opn + '-stock'); el.innerText = inStockText; el = document.getElementById(opn + '-limit'); if (orderLimit < 999999999) { el.innerText = el.innerText + ' ' + orderLimit; } else { el.parentElement.removeChild(el); } } else { /* out of stock */ el = document.getElementById(opn + '-cart'); el.parentElement.removeChild(el); el = document.getElementById(opn + '-price'); /* price element may not exist */ el && el.parentElement.removeChild(el); el = document.getElementById(opn + '-stock'); el.classList.add('u-font-weight-heavy'); el.innerText = outOfStockText; el = document.getElementById(opn + '-limit'); el.parentElement.removeChild(el); } availableEl.style.display = 'block'; } } }); }; /** * Apply "not logged in" behaviour. */ var setLoginRequired = function (toolsList) { toolsList.forEach(function (opn) { var availableEl = document.getElementById(opn + '-available'); if (availableEl) { var el = document.getElementById(opn + '-cart'); el.parentElement.removeChild(el); el = document.getElementById(opn + '-orderable'); el.parentElement.removeChild(el); el = document.getElementById(opn + '-unavailable'); el.parentElement.removeChild(el); el = document.getElementById(opn + '-order'); /* set login link return url hash to '#design-development' */ el.querySelector('a').href = '/secure-link-forward/?gotoUrl=' + encodeURIComponent(window.location.origin + window.location.pathname + window.location.search + '#design-development'); el = document.getElementById(opn + '-view'); /* set login link return url hash to '#design-development' */ el.querySelector('a').href = '/secure-link-forward/?gotoUrl=' + encodeURIComponent(window.location.origin + window.location.pathname + window.location.search + '#design-development'); availableEl.style.display = 'block'; } }); }; /** * If inventory response is an error - remove inventory dom. */ var setToolsUnavailable = function (toolsList) { toolsList.forEach(function (opn) { var el = document.getElementById(opn + '-available'); el && el.parentElement.removeChild(el); }); }; window.addEventListener("tiCurrencyChange", currencyUpdate); window.addEventListener("tiCurrencyReady", currencyUpdate); window.addEventListener("tiLanguageChange", localeUpdate); window.addEventListener("tiLanguageReady", localeUpdate); window.addEventListener('tiCurrencyFormatReady', setCurrencyFormat); if (document.readyState === 'complete') { loadToolsInventory(); setCurrencyFormat(); } else { window.addEventListener('load', function () { loadToolsInventory(); setCurrencyFormat(); }); } /*]]>*/ </script> <div class="ti_p-row"> <div class="ti_p-col-12"> <style> ti-tab-container:not(.hydrated) { position: relative; } </style> <ti-tab-container all-tab-shown data-lid="folder_product_design_and_development_tab" hash-selection all-tab-title="All" selected-tab-id="all" > <ti-tab-panel id="tab2" data-lid="folder_product_design_tools_simulation" data-navtitle="Design tools &amp; simulation" tab-title="Design tools &amp; simulation" tab-id="design-tools-simulation" > <!-- /* Message for > 10 Reference Design Assets */--> <!-- /* Asset items */ --> <div class="u-divide-y mod-no-top-line"> <!-- /* Responsive rows */ --> <div class="u-padding-vertical-4" > <div class="ti_p-row u-margin-horizontal-0"> <div class="ti_p-col-2 ti_p-col-phone-12 u-ie-flex-basis-auto"> <div class="ti_p-asset-image mod-illustrative-icon"> <ti-image ratio="rectangle" src="/content/dam/ticom/images/icons/illustrative-icons/industrial/graph-icon.png" ></ti-image> </div> </div> <div class="ti_p-col-8 mod-row-space-phone"> <div class="u-font-size-small u-text-uppercase u-margin-bottom-2">Simulation model</div> <h4 class="u-text-breakword u-margin-bottom-4" > <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="u-font-weight-normal" href="/lit/zip/sbvm035" data-navtitle="simulation model|TLV803M Unencrypted PSpice Transient Model Package (Rev. A)" >TLV803M Unencrypted PSpice Transient Model Package (Rev. A)</a> </h4> <div class="u-margin-top-4">SBVM035A.ZIP (50 KB) - PSpice Model</div> </div> <div class="ti_p-col ti_p-col-phone-12 mod-row-space-phone u-text-left u-ie-flex-basis-auto"> <ti-button class="u-fullWidth u-margin-bottom-2" appearance="primary compact"> <a class="u-fullWidth u-text-center" data-navtitle="simulation model-SBVM035A.ZIP (50 KB) - PSpice Model-Download" href="/lit/zip/sbvm035" > <span style="white-space: normal;">Download</span> </a> </ti-button> </div> </div> </div> <!-- /* Responsive rows */ --> <div class="u-padding-vertical-4" > <div class="ti_p-row u-margin-horizontal-0"> <div class="ti_p-col-2 ti_p-col-phone-12 u-ie-flex-basis-auto"> <div class="ti_p-asset-image mod-illustrative-icon"> <ti-image ratio="rectangle" src="/content/dam/ticom/images/icons/illustrative-icons/software/simulation-tools-icon.png" ></ti-image> </div> </div> <div class="ti_p-col-8 mod-row-space-phone"> <div class="u-font-size-small u-text-uppercase u-margin-bottom-2">Simulation tool</div> <h4 class="u-text-breakword u-margin-bottom-4" > <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="u-font-weight-normal" href="/tool/PSPICE-FOR-TI" data-navtitle="Simulation tool|PSPICE-FOR-TI" >PSPICE-FOR-TI</a> <span class="u-font-weight-light" > — PSpice® for TI design and simulation tool</span> </h4> <div class="u-margin-bottom-0 u-paragraph-medium" >PSpice&reg; for TI is a design and simulation environment that helps evaluate functionality of analog circuits. This full-featured, design and simulation suite uses an analog analysis engine from Cadence&reg;. Available at no cost, PSpice for TI includes one of the largest model libraries in the (...)</div> </div> <div class="ti_p-col ti_p-col-phone-12 mod-row-space-phone u-text-left u-ie-flex-basis-auto"> <ti-button appearance="primary compact" class="u-fullWidth u-margin-bottom-2"> <a class="u-fullWidth u-text-center" data-navtitle="simulation tool-PSPICE-FOR-TI-Request" href="https://www.ti.com/event/docs/accesseventaction.tsp?actionId=3228" style="white-space: normal;" target="_blank" >Request</a> </ti-button> </div> </div> </div> </div> <!-- /* CAD/CAE Table */ --> </ti-tab-panel><ti-tab-panel id="tab4" data-lid="folder_product_cad_cae_symbols" data-navtitle="CAD symbols, footprints &amp; 3D models" tab-title="CAD symbols, footprints &amp; 3D models" tab-id="cad-cae-symbols" > <!-- /* Message for > 10 Reference Design Assets */--> <!-- /* Asset items */ --> <div class="u-divide-y mod-no-top-line"> </div> <!-- /* CAD/CAE Table */ --> <ti-table-controller columns="package, pins, CAD symbols, footprints & 3D models" > <table id="tbl-cad-cae"> <colgroup> <col style="width:280px" /> <col style="width:200px" /> <col style="width:800px" /> </colgroup> <thead> <tr> <th >Package</th> <th >Pins</th> <th >CAD symbols, footprints &amp; 3D models</th> </tr> </thead> <tbody> <tr > <td > <a id="cad_cae_symbol_0_package" href="/lit/pdf/mpds108g" target="_blank" >SOT-23 (DBZ)</a> </td> <td>3</td> <td > <a id="cad_cae_symbol_0_view" data-navtitle="SOT-23 (DBZ)-Ultra Librarian" href="https://vendor.ultralibrarian.com/TI/embedded/?gpn=TLV863M&amp;package=DBZ&amp;pin=3" target="_blank" >Ultra Librarian</a> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> </ti-table-controller> </ti-tab-panel> </ti-tab-container> <div class="u-margin-top-8"> <a href="/legal/terms-of-sale.html">TI's Standard Terms and Conditions for Evaluation Items apply.</a> </div> </div> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> /* * Purpose: This next set of functions contains pure JS functions * to update/append tiSessionID and consent cookie flag to CAD/CAE URL * that apply to the product folder single-page experience project. * Created: 3/16/2020 */ function readDistCookie(cookieName) { var cookieName = cookieName + "="; var cookiesArr = document.cookie.split(";"); for (var i = 0; i < cookiesArr.length; i++) { var iCookie = cookiesArr[i]; while (iCookie.charAt(0) === " ") { iCookie = iCookie.substring(1, iCookie.length) } if (iCookie.indexOf(cookieName) === 0) { return iCookie.substring(cookieName.length, iCookie.length) } } return null } function getConsentCookie() { var consentFlag = 0; var consentCookie = decodeURIComponent(readDistCookie("CONSENTMGR")); if(!consentCookie) { return consentFlag; } if(consentCookie.indexOf("c1:") > -1) { var splitCookies = consentCookie.split("|"); for(var i = 0; i < splitCookies.length; i++) { if(splitCookies[i].indexOf("c1:") === 0) { consentFlag = splitCookies[i].split(":")[1]; break; } } } else { consentFlag = 1; } return consentFlag; } function updateCadCaeUltralibrarianUrl(id, col) { var tableEl = document.querySelector("#" + id); if(tableEl) { var tiSessionIdCookie = ""; if(readDistCookie("tiSessionID")) { tiSessionIdCookie = readDistCookie("tiSessionID"); } var consentCookie = getConsentCookie(); for (var i = 1; i < tableEl.rows.length; i++) { var anchorEl = tableEl.rows[i].cells[col].getElementsByTagName("a")[0]; anchorEl.setAttribute("href", anchorEl.getAttribute("href") + "&sid=" + tiSessionIdCookie + "&c=" + consentCookie); } } } updateCadCaeUltralibrarianUrl("tbl-cad-cae", 2); </script> <div class="ti_p-row"> <div class="ti_p-col-12 u-margin-top-8"> <ti-main-panel data-lid="odt_panel" base-url="https://product-odt-panel.ti.com" gpn="TLV863M" locale="en-US" class="u-fullWidth u-margin-top-6" ></ti-main-panel> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section> <div class="ti_p-page-responsive"> <div class="ti_p-row"> <div class="ti_p-col-12"> <h3 navbar-id="order-quality" navbar-name="Ordering &amp; quality" data-navtitle="Ordering &amp; quality" class="u-text-center u-text-left-only-on-phone u-header-2">Ordering &amp; quality</h3> </div> </div> </div> <div> <ti-order-now-table data-lid="product_folder_samplebuy_table" generic-part-number="TLV863M" locale="en-US" sticky-header-offset="90" store-url="/product/TLV863M/part-details/" page-length="all" > <script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"Product","name":"TLV863M","description":"3-pin voltage supervisor with active-low open-drain reset in reverse pin out","mpn":"TLV863M","sku":"TLV863M","brand":"TI","additionalProperty":[{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"addToCartUrls","valueReference":[{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"apiUrl","value":"https://www.ti.com/recaptchaproxy/occservices/v2/ti/addtocart"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"checkoutUrl","value":"https://www.ti.com/occservices/v2/ti/redirect2HybrisCart?CartId="},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"customReelsApiUrl","value":"/productmodel/customreel/inventoryforecast"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"descriptionApiUrl","value":"/popularorderables/addtocart/"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"tiStoreCnUrl","value":"https://www.ti.com.cn"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"tiStoreUrl","value":"https://www.ti.com"}]},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"labelTexts","valueReference":[{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"allText","value":"All"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"alternateSampleText","value":"Alternate sample"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"americasText","value":"Americas"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"amiUrlTooltip","value":"Information included:"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"asiaText","value":"Asia"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"carrierDialogMessage","value":"<div><p><strong>You can choose different carrier options based on the quantity of parts, including full reel, custom reel, cut tape, tube or tray.</strong></p><p>A <strong>custom reel</strong> is a continuous length of cut tape from one reel to maintain lot- and date-code traceability, built to the exact quantity requested. Following industry standards, a brass shim connects an 18-inch leader and trailer on both sides of the cut tape for direct feeding into automated assembly machines. TI includes a reeling fee for custom reel orders.</p><p><strong>Cut tape</strong> is a length of tape cut from a reel. TI may fulfill orders using multiple strips of cut tapes or boxes to satisfy the quantity requested.</p><p>TI often ships <strong>tube</strong> or <strong>tray</strong> devices inside a box or in the tube or tray, depending on inventory availability. We pack all tapes, tubes or sample boxes according to internal electrostatic discharge and moisture-sensitivity-level protection requirements.</p><a href=\"/ordering-resources/carrier-packaging-options.html\">Learn more</a></div>"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"carrierDialogTitle","value":"Carrier options"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"contactTIUrl","value":"/guidedsupport/call-ti-support"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"cscUrl","value":"https://ticsc.service-now.com/csm"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"custom","value":"CUSTOM"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"customReelTooltip","value":"Custom reel may be available"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"enterQuantityText","value":"Enter quantity"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"europeText","value":"Europe"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"filterText","value":"Filter"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"futureInventoryText","value":"Future inventory"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"limitMessage","value":"This limit is in place to protect sample purchases for design evaluation and will be removed once more stock is available."},{"@type":"PropertyValue","name":"limitText","value":"Limit:"},{"@type":"PropertyValue","nam